title: Race 3
subTitle: The thirst for power drives a wealthy family to become rivals in a risky heist. As a consequence, they face betrayal and danger along the way.

title: Taaqat
subTitle: Two gangsters working for politicians from opposite parties believe that their respective leaders will provide a better future. The two are pitted against each other when the politicians unite.

title: Ru-Ba-Ru
subTitle: Tara and Nikhil are in a relationship and the former wants to take their relationship to the next step. However, Nikhil's work ambitions poses challenges for them.

title: Khuda Kasam
subTitle: CBI Officer Neetu Singh is framed for the assassination of a chief minister. She then attempts to solve this murder mystery with the help of a man, who is imprisoned for a crime he never committed.

title: Mere Sajna Saath Nibhana
subTitle: Kanhaiya, a poor street performer, falls in love with Chanchal, a wealthy woman. He convinces his mother to ask for her hand in marriage, but things take a turn when Chanchal's father insults her.

title: Dil Ka Kya Kasoor
subTitle: A rich girl, Shalini, falls in love with an orphan, Arun, after he performs the poems she wrote using a pen name. However, things take a tragic turn when Arun marries the principal's daughter, Meena.

title: Haan Maine Bhi Pyaar Kiya
subTitle: Pooja divorces her husband for being unfaithful and gets a job as secretary to a film star. The two fall in love, before her ex-husband returns and she finds herself confused between the two men.

title: Janta Ki Adalat
subTitle: DSP Jyoti foils the plans of Shankar, a prisoner who threatens to kill a minister. But she lends her support to Shankar after she hears about the minister's dark secrets and ill intentions.

title: Chori Chori Chupke Chupke
subTitle: Raj and Priya, a married couple, hire Madhubala, a prostitute, as the surrogate mother of their child. Trouble brews when Madhubala falls in love with Raj and insists on keeping the child.

title: Apna Sapna Money Money
subTitle: Arjun and Shivani are in love, but Shivani's father will never let them marry each other. Later chaos ensues when Arjun enlists the help of his conman cousin, Kishan, to unite him with Shivani.

title: Apna Sapna Money Money
subTitle: Arjun and Shivani are in love, but Shivani's father will never let them marry each other. Later chaos ensues when Arjun enlists the help of his conman cousin, Kishan, to unite him with Shivani.

title: Issaq
subTitle: In the kaleidoscopic cityscapes of Banaras, a soul-stirring Romeo-and-Juliet-esque romance kindles between two young individuals from rival mafia families.

title: Drohi
subTitle: Krishna, a cop, is assigned the responsibility of tracking down a notorious hitman, Raghav. He finds himself in a dilemma when he discovers that his sister is in love with Raghav.

title: Ghajini
subTitle: Suffering from memory loss every 15 minutes, a heartbroken man uses photographs, notes and tattoos to keep reminding himself to punish his lady-love's murderer.

title: Crew
subTitle: Three ambitious female cabin attendants from Mumbai get caught in a web of lies during their pursuit of dreams, leading to an unexpected heist.

title: Tyagi
subTitle: Shankar, a good man, takes the blame when one of his brothers is accused of a murder. However, when he returns from jail, he realises that his brothers are trying to create a rift in the family.

title: Ek Rishtaa: The Bond of Love
subTitle: Amid the ideological differences with his father Vijay, Ajay steps up to protect his family from Rajesh's, his brother-in-law's, evil intentions.

title: Bholaa
subTitle: After getting out of prison with the desire to meet his daughter, Bholaa's plans are interrupted by a well-orchestrated drug bust.

title: Karan Arjun
subTitle: Karan and Arjun, two brothers driven by revenge, are murdered by their uncle while seeking justice for their father's death. However, they resurrect years later to settle their unfinished score.

title: Jurm
subTitle: SHEKHAR IS A POLICE OFFICER IN THE BOMBAY POLICE FORCE. HE IS A HONEST AND DEDICATED MAN MARRIED TO MEENA FROM HER A DAUGHTER BABLI- THEY MAKE AN ENVIABLE FAMILY. KADAM, HIS JUNIOR OFFICER IS THE ONLY REAL FRIEND HE HAS. ALL IS WELL WITH SHEKHAR AND THEN SUDDENLY ONE DAY HIS LIFE BEGINS TO FALL APRT. EDITOR RITESH NANDY IS KILLED.

title: Prem Deewane
subTitle: A young couple in love run away together after their parents oppose their relationship. They are misguided into kidnapping a wealthy person for a big ransom by a shrewd uncle who has his own agenda.

title: Police Aur Mujrim
subTitle: After DSP Vishal arrests two thugs, their boss kidnaps the commissioner's daughter. But after Vishal rescues the girl and jails the thugs, they return to hurt Vishal and the commissioner's families.

title: Kasam Suhaag Ki
subTitle: Troubles arise for Surajmukhi after her husband, Sultan, is gunned down and she and her daughter get abducted by goons. She tries her best to get revenge and escape with her child.

title: Hamara Dil Aapke Paas Hai
subTitle: When Preeti stands up against a murderer in court, she suffers a devastating consequence. Later, after being rejected by her loved ones, she finds shelter and support in an empathetic stranger.

title: Hero No. 1
subTitle: Rajesh and Meena intend to marry each other, but her grandfather disapproves of their relationship. Soon, he poses himself as a servant and enters her home to try and win the approval of her loved one's using his wit and talent.

title: Khatta Meetha
subTitle: A seemingly corrupt petty contractor faces challenges from the local municipality, his family, his employees, as well as a former girlfriend and her family.

title: Tirangaa
subTitle: Brigadier Suryadev Singh and Shivajirao Waghle, a police inspector, work together to track down a terrorist who plans to evade India.

title: Daanveer
subTitle: Vijay, an orphan, is tasked with raising his siblings, Vishal and Sudha. Later, Sudha is disowned by her in-laws and Vishal falls for the enemy's daughter but Vijay comes to their rescue.
